---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import FAQSchema from "../../../components/FAQSchema.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Carpet Cleaning Boucherville | Prestige Homes & Business Park"
  description="The expert in carpet and upholstery cleaning in Boucherville. Tailored solutions for luxury residences and corporate offices in the industrial park."
>
  <!-- SPLIT SCREEN HERO -->
  <div class="split-hero-container">
    <div class="container full-width-split">
      <div class="split-layout">
        <!-- LEFT COLUMN: CONTENT (Hook) -->
        <div class="split-content fade-in-section">
          <span class="service-cat-badge">PRESTIGE LEVEL • BOUCHERVILLE</span>
          <h1 class="split-title fade-in-up text-gradient-empire">
            Carpet & Upholstery Cleaning in Boucherville
          </h1>

          <div class="problem-statement fade-in-up delay-100" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent);">
            <h3 class="problem-title" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Exceptional Properties:</h3>
            <p class="problem-text">
              The vast residences of Boucherville often feature high-quality wall-to-wall carpeting, delicate oriental rugs, and luxurious upholstered furniture. Near the river or in premium neighborhoods, seasonal humidity and indoor dust demand meticulous maintenance to protect your investments.
            </p>
          </div>

          <p class="lead-text fade-in-up delay-200">
            Known for our discretion and the sheer power of our truck-mount units, our certified technicians bring your interiors back to life. Whether it’s a heritage century-old home, a modern estate, or corporate offices in the industrial park, we are the local authority in deep cleaning.
          </p>

          <div class="cta-group fade-in-up delay-300">
            <a href="tel:5148939939" class="btn btn-gradient-green pulse-btn">
              <span class="icon">📞</span> (514) 893-9939 (Boucherville Service)
            </a>
            <button
              onclick="window.openEstimationWidget()"
              class="btn btn-gradient-green"
            >
              <span class="icon">⚡</span> Fast & Free Online Quote
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT COLUMN: IMAGE (Visual / Slideshow) -->
        <div class="split-image-wrapper fade-in-section delay-200">
          <div class="slideshow-container">
             <img
              src="/images/catalog/nettoyage-fauteuil-professionnel.webp"
              alt="Professional furniture cleaning in a Boucherville home"
              class="slide active"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              fetchpriority="high"
              loading="eager"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/nettoyage-tapis-vapeur-laval.webp"
              alt="Empire Cleaning truck-mount deployed in Boucherville"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
             <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-40.webp"
              alt="Upholstered living room furniture cleaned by steam extraction"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="image-overlay-gradient"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-layout">
        <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
        <div class="service-main">
          <!-- BENEFIT LIST & SEO CONTENT -->
          <div class="fade-in-section delay-100">
            <h2 class="section-title text-gradient-empire">
              Why Does Boucherville Choose Empire Cleaning Group?
            </h2>

            <p>
              Our approach merges advanced cleaning science with industrial-grade equipment, ensuring results that far exceed traditional or rental methods:
            </p>

            <ul class="benefit-list" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
              <li>
                <strong>The Truck-Mount Advantage:</strong> Our units independently heat water to nearly 230°F (110°C). This extreme heat melts embedded greases and oils without flooding your floors, completely recovered by our titanic suction power.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Delicate Fabric Care:</strong> Designer furniture and genuine wool rugs require special skills. We use a low-pH conditioner to prevent color migration (bleeding) of your valuable area rugs.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Absolute Sanitization:</strong> Our thermal extraction literally eradicates dust mites, microscopic mold spores, and allergens brought in by pets.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Commercial and Industrial Sector:</strong> Boucherville hosts one of the largest industrial parks in Quebec. Our night-shift crews intervene to sanitize your office carpets and conference chairs with zero downtime for your operations.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Lightning-Fast Drying:</strong> Thanks to the overpowering vacuum of our truck-mounts, your carpets are generally completely dry in 3 to 5 hours, a major achievement for large square-footage homes.
              </li>
            </ul>

            <div style="margin-top: 3rem; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px;">
               <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                🌱 Eco-Responsible Commitment
              </h3>
              <p>
                Living near the beautiful Saint Lawrence River, our Boucherville clients are environmentally conscious. The primary cleaning agents we deploy are certified non-toxic, devoid of heavy detergents, and perfectly safe for septic systems and municipal waterways on the South Shore.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: 3rem;">
              <hr class="separator" />
              <h3>Stain Removal and Emergencies</h3>
              <p>
                A glass of red wine spilled during a dinner party? A new puppy in training? Don't wait and <strong>do not scrub the fiber</strong>. Read our <a href="/en/tips/erreurs-taches-tapis" style="color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: bold;">emergency stain guide</a> and call us right away. Our truck-mounts are frequently patrolling Route 132!
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NEW SECTIONS: BENEFITS & FAQ -->
  <section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-layout" style="display: block;">
        <div class="service-main" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
           
           <!-- ZONES DESSERVIES -->
          <div class="zones-section" style="margin-top: 3rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
            <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.4rem;">Rapid Intervention Everywhere in Boucherville</h3>

             <div class="city-group">
              <div class="badges-container">
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Old Boucherville (Heritage Sector)</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Boucherville Industrial Park</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Harmonie Sector</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Les Boisés</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Riverside Estates (Fleuve)</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Varennes (Nearby)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="contact-footer">Secure your appointment slot today: <strong>(514) 893-9939</strong>.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ -->
          <div class="fade-in-section delay-300" style="margin-top: 3rem;">
            <h2 class="section-title text-gradient-empire">
              Frequently Asked Questions — Boucherville Clients
            </h2>
            <FAQSchema
              faqs={[
                 {
                  question:
                    "Do you clean large expanses of commercial carpeting in our Boucherville industrial park office?",
                  answer:
                    "Absolutely. Our experienced commercial professionals are equipped for vast commercial zones with flexible evening or weekend scheduling, causing zero downtime for your employees the next day.",
                },
                {
                  question:
                    "I have a very large home and my outdoor water hoses are already shut off for winter. Is this an issue?",
                  answer:
                    "Not at all. Our truck-mounts are 100% self-sufficient in deep winter. We bring our own supply of pre-heated water from our facility and extract the soiled water back into our truck without ever needing your exterior hoses.",
                },
                {
                   question:
                    "Do you guarantee the removal of completely black traffic lanes on a light-colored dining room carpet?",
                  answer:
                    "Oil stains, dressing, and heavy traffic lanes are highly treatable using our aggressive alkaline pre-treatment combined with 200°F+ extraction. Barring permanent dye loss or fiber burns, our success rate is exceptional.",
                },
                {
                  question:
                    "Do you clean imported Persian or pure silk area rugs?",
                  answer:
                    "Yes, but our method differs completely from synthetic wall-to-wall carpeting. We will evaluate the pH of the natural dye in your wool or silk rug to prevent any bleeding before applying a specialized, gentle extraction process.",
                }
              ]}
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<script>
  const slides = document.querySelectorAll(".slide");
  if (slides.length > 0) {
    let currentSlide = 0;
    setInterval(() => {
      slides[currentSlide].classList.remove("active");
      currentSlide = (currentSlide + 1) % slides.length;
      slides[currentSlide].classList.add("active");
    }, 4000);
  }
</script>

<style>
  /* Base styles reused for consistency */
  .split-hero-container { background-color: #fff; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; overflow: hidden; width: 100vw; }
  .full-width-split { width: 100%; max-width: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .split-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0; align-items: stretch; min-height: 80vh; }
  .split-content { background-color: #ffffff; padding: 100px 4rem 4rem 10%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  .service-cat-badge { text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 0.85rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .split-title { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 3.5vw, 4rem); color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.1; }
  .city-group { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .badges-container { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .badge { padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; border: 1px solid transparent; }
  .badge-blue { background: #e8f4fd; border-color: #c5dff0; }
  .problem-statement { background: #ffffff; border-left: 4px solid #ff4444; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0; margin-bottom: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(174, 206, 235, 0.3); }
  .problem-title { font-size: 1rem; color: #cc0000; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; }
  .problem-text { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--color-text-main); font-style: italic; }
  .lead-text { font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--color-text-main); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; max-width: 650px; }
  .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .cta-group { display: none !important; } }
  .split-image-wrapper { position: relative; height: 100%; min-height: 500px; width: 100%; }
  .slideshow-container { position: relative; width: 100%; height: 100%; overflow: hidden; }
  .slideshow-container img.slide {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100% !important;
    height: 100% !important;
    object-fit: cover !important;
    object-position: center !important;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 1.5s ease-in-out;
  }
  .slideshow-container img.slide.active { opacity: 1; }
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .split-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; min-height: auto; }
    .split-content { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; order: 1; }
    .split-image-wrapper { order: 2; height: 400px; min-height: 0; }
    .lead-text { max-width: 100%; }
  }
  .service-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 5rem; }
  .section-title { font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; display: inline-block; }
  .separator { border: 0; height: 1px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  .benefit-list { margin: 2rem 0; list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .benefit-list li { margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .benefit-list li::before { content: "✓"; color: #d32f2f; position: absolute; left: 0; font-weight: bold; }
  .contact-footer { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-style: italic; color: #666; }
</style>
